    {"text": "Aphids on mustard crop: spray dimethoate 30 EC @ 1 ml/L or neem-based pesticide. Introduce ladybird beetles as biological control.", "source": "ICAR Pest Alert", "category": "pest"},
    {"text": "Cotton Bollworm (Helicoverpa armigera): use pheromone traps @ 5/ha. Spray Emamectin benzoate 5% SG @ 0.4 g/L. Avoid continuous cotton monoculture.", "source": "ICAR Pest Alert", "category": "pest"},
